Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who had it all,\NPirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His final words spurred people\Nto take to the seas in droves:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've left everything\Nthis world's got to offer {\i1}there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so men set sail for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the world is in the midst\Nof the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Having defeated\NDuval's Flying Fish Riders,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy and company\Nnow head for Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't mean\Nyou're suddenly somehow forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering how it tastes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! It is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First, there are actually two routes\Nthat lead to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But for outlaws like you guys,\Nthere's really only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just maintain course\Nfor the route you'll use,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,which is known as Fishman Island's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sea Floor Route"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Line is a large barrier\Nthat stretches all around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is one small hole\Nin one part of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's where Fishman Island is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to make their ship\Ncapable of submerging to the sea floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and company\Nneeded to visit a certain island first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabaody Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It came outta the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm riding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's our purpose\Non this island, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're going to see\Na coating craftsman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and have him cover your ship in resin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put, that'll make it\Nso your ship can go underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And so Luffy and company landed\Non Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to find a coating craftsman Hachi knows.
