Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's gone into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, we used up all the cola\Nin that last sea battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's maintenance is my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm stayin' behind\Nbecause I wanna help, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all three of us\Ngo when we're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This island looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna wait for someone to come back\Nand then go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because my beloved\NNami-san said this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever will I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship is so full\Nof treasure right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish there was a knight somewhere\Nwho could protect it for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure know how to fall\Nright into Nami's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a slave of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Admitting it yourself saves me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth to Zoro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going all by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare, you damn bastard!\NYou always get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an archipelago, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never be able to find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't gonna get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As if anyone could get lost on such\Nstraightforward islands as these!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All the trees are numbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Worst case, even a kid could make\Nit back by asking for directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected you\Nto have such street-smarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We underestimated you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to ask for directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't trust yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno what the hell\Nthey're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to remember\Nthis tree's number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,#1. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They can mock me all they want;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never get lost on these islands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike some other guy\Nwith no sense of direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The World Nobles are also known\Nas the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They act so high and mighty\Nthat they wear masks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep from breathing\Nthe same air as common people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't defy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one thing you have to promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a couple other things\Nto watch out for, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I mentioned before,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,people heading for the New World\Ngather on these islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There are infamous\Npirates like you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as marines and bounty hunters\Nwho are out to catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no law here at all\Nagainst buying and selling pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do anything to stand out\Nand they'll set their sights on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so be very careful what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The marines here\Naren't pushovers, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Navy Headquarters is in\Nnearby waters, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why the bounty hunters\Nare all just as ferocious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And one other thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There are too many things\Nto watch out for!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, when did you get hurt there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie and I aren't Merfolk or Fishmen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat us like we're human\Non these islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll make things a lot simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When in a city,\Ndo as its citizens do, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do as Mr. Octopus says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Harder! And push into it slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get in! I can get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not leaking at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that high enough for ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll go forward now if you peddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's going forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It really doesn't pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Convenient, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Sabaody Archipelago's\Nfamous bubble bikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.92,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wanna ride too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 500 berries a day to rent one,\Nor 10,000 berries to buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty cheap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we'll rent--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy this one\Nwith my spending money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just rent.\NThere's no point in buying one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you get to decide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Urgh! I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll rent two more, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're from around these parts?\NWhat a bummer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it, though?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They even have different kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me want to sing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm gonna buy\Na bubble bike after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how you first went up\Ninto the sky on those bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come falling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Actually, I went\Npast the tops of the trees
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and wondered if I could\Ngo any higher up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...when all the bubbles\Naround me disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the bubble I was on\Nsuddenly popped too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have left\NSabaody Archipelago's climate area, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has a suitable climate\Nfor Hustle Mustle Mangroves to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside that area,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the resin components in the bubbles\Nlose a lot of their capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means the bubbles\Ncan't be ridden outside of these islands?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Newcomers here often buy bubble bikes\Nand take them with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dirty business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Renting bubble bikes is all you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm buying one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I can't agree\Nwith that explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't understand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, the bubbles will pop\Noutside of these islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,mysteriously enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! They pop mysteriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been trying to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can use it on\NFishman Island, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bubble civilization\Non the sea floor, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to Fishman Island\Nright away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should meet\Nthe Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a girl of matchless beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a panderer; shall I hook you up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I love having an eyeful\Nof beautiful girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I lack eyes,\Ndue to being a skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, that smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a "Grand-Bun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.08,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Grand-Bun" "GR Famous Food!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.33,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"GR Famous Grand-Choco!!" "GR Famous Grand-Bun!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:13:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Line Manju buns!\NCommonly called Grand-Buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a taste test?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See how they say\N"Grandline First Half" here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very popular as souvenirs\Nfor going into the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They last for three whole months,\Nso you can rest easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,These are delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you to open the next box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to pay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Grove #35.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There seem to be a lot of hotels here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're for the sailors who're waiting\Nfor their passes from Mary Geoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Building hotels is easy, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,See, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Paint a giant bubble with a metal alloy\Nand you have your foundation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how round buildings are made!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Is that a shopping mall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand-cracker! Grand-choco!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Keychain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:13:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pennant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are all about the memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You really bought a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be tough to lug all that around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have 'im bubble pack it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bubble pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need strength\Nto carry stuff on these islands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are Nami and Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They went to the shopping mall\Nin Grove #30.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They left us in charge\Nof getting the ship coated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? They did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we headed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Grove #13.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a ways away,\Neven by bubble bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie-chan didn't come along\Nwhen we invited her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been a bit reserved\Never since we landed on these islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's up with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows, perhaps this island\Nhas a bad history...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad history?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the lead now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a long way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Hatchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this suddenly\Nturn into a race?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,U-uhh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Take...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...going back home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Hey!\NI beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just lend me an axe or a saw
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to break this collar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've given up on the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a wife and kid back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Please!\NHelp me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid was just a baby back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The bugger still doesn't\Neven know what I look like!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get involved, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably a pirate who was caught\Nby kidnappers and then sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,His owners brought him to this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he surely knows\Nthere's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn this collar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If only... If only it wasn't for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaves always have leashes\Naround their necks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that are set to explode if the slaves\Ntry to remove them and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna buy souvenirs and go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving up the pirate business...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an escaped slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get involved with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! We need to help that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised not to get involved,\Nno matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatchin! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are Celestial Dragons nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay calm, Camie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come down from the bubble bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Celestial Dra--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You kneel down, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever comes,\Ndon't look them in the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for you guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! How disgraceful, Saruu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one has broken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you remember to give it\Na sedative every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I most certainly did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no effect on the poor fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please buy me a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're terrible at taking care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep breaking everything\Nin my ship captain collection...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this thing's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A grown man, always crying\Nabout family this, family that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When he's nothing but a mere human!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not doing anything now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,--She's--!\N--Stop! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I would like\Na Giant for a slave next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you will start with a human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like such weak ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Just endure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get out of here for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It will help you relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel very good now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'll survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he does,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll probably go to prison,\Nseeing that he's a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That pirate could've easily\Nbeaten that old man and lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Harm a Celestial Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and a Navy HQ admiral\Nwill lead an entire army here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,An admiral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Pheasant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It could even be Red Hound or Yellow Monkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Navy Headquarters\Nis very close by, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes them so high and mighty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They share the Creators' blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Creators?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The twenty kings who created the huge\NWorld Government organization
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,800 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Their descendents are\Nthe Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With each passing generation,\Nthey grow more reckless with power,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,which is why they act like that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,300 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.19,0:23:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakky's Rip-Off Bar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey-chan, is it? Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I would know of the 300 million berries, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are currently,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,people with higher bounties than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher than Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"New Rivals Gather!\NThe Eleven Supernovas"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.39,0:23:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
